OL,3,C'Political movement' formed in
OL,4,CGuernsey ahead of 2025 election
OL,6,FGuernsey's Former Chief Minister is
OL,7,Fexpected to begin a new political
OL,8,Fgrouping with a shared policy platform
OL,9,Fahead of next year's States election.
OL,11,FDeputy Gavin St Pier will unveil
OL,12,FFuture Guernsey at 6pm on Thursday 28
OL,13,FNovember with more than 250 people
OL,14,Fexpected to attend the event at the
OL,15,FPerforming Arts Centre.
OL,17,FThe organisation will set policies
OL,18,Fbased on six key areas: housing,
OL,19,Fhealthcare, education, the economy,
OL,20,Fthe environment and fiscal
OL,21,Fresponsibility.
