OL,6,FITV News understands no current
OL,7,Fdeputies have been approached to join
OL,8,Fthe organisation.
OL,10,FIf any deputies are elected under the
OL,11,Fbanner of 'Future Guernsey', they will
OL,12,Fvote as a group on key policies.
OL,14,FHowever, the organisation is not being
OL,15,Fregistered as a political party, and
OL,16,Fit is not yet known which side of the
OL,17,Fpolitical spectrum it will represent.
