OL,6,FGavin St Pier will serve as the
OL,7,Forganisation's 'political advisor',
OL,8,Fwith former ITN chief executive John
OL,9,FHardie as its chairman, and
OL,10,Fcommunications consultant Lindsey
OL,11,FFreeman as CEO.
OL,13,FDeputy St Pier said: "The fact that
OL,14,Fonly 13% of islanders we spoke to as
OL,15,Fpart of our research, about one in 10,
OL,16,Fthinks that our political system is
OL,17,Fworking can hardly be a great surprise
OL,18,Fto anyone.
