OL,6,F"We cannot carry on as we are and we
OL,7,Fcannot afford another four years with
OL,8,Fas much indecision and inaction as
OL,9,Fthis political term. The time for
OL,10,Fchange is now."
OL,12,FWhat does Future Guernsey stand for?
OL,13,FThat's the important question to ask
OL,14,Fand the one that doesn't really have
OL,15,Fan answer... yet.
OL,17,FWhat has been made very clear during
OL,18,Fthe last few elections is that people
OL,19,Fvote on very specific issues.
